{"tid":690543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"央視又打臉？國產與國外作業系統差距還有多大？","createTime":"2018-06-05T03:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T10:48:33.000Z","uid":31744,"like":70,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"d6797418701fe2a8bf0007d35ba1c6891dcfe8a1","tid":690543,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:27:18.000Z","msg":"在直播的這欄節目中，知名央視主持人陳偉鴻在現場做了小小的盲測，在沒有告知作業系統的前提下，在現場對比了兩款筆記本的頁面載入速度。而根據右側的Chrome頁面載入速度快於左側的IE流覽器，從而得出國產系統快於國外系統的&ldquo;偽科學&rdquo;結果，引起了廣大網友的質疑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/112420_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F112420_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=e6052d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近期央視二套財經節目中，進行了一場令人尷尬的對比。在標題為&ldquo;實力比拼：國產系統PK國外系統&rdquo;的對比中，在存在多種影響因素的情況下得出了&ldquo;國產系統快於國外系統&rdquo;的結果。<br />\n<br />\n在直播的這欄節目中，知名央視主持人陳偉鴻在現場做了小小的盲測，在沒有告知作業系統的前提下，在現場對比了兩款筆記本的頁面載入速度。而根據右側的Chrome頁面載入速度快於左側的IE流覽器，從而得出國產系統快於國外系統的&ldquo;偽科學&rdquo;結果，引起了廣大網友的質疑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/112610_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F112610_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=33faaf5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/112610_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F112610_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=54922c9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/112610_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F112610_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=fcd479c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de2e8f2b63487eca394